# This is the directory the running api container reads mapping
# documents from at boot. The default SENTRY_INBOUND_MAPPINGS_DIR
# (`db/mappings`) resolves to /app/db/mappings inside the api
# container, which bind-mounts to ./api/db/mappings/ on the host.
#
# Operators writing their first mapping doc: start with
# `example-template.yaml.template` in this directory. Copy to
# `<source_system>.yaml`, edit, drop in an inbound_source_systems_allowlist
# row, restart api.
#
# See issue #279 for the documentation drift between this directory
# and the repo-root `db/mappings/` (whose .gitkeep also claims to be
# the operative path).
